data.description: Why wait to build when you can have this one owner new home now!  A stunning rare find with it's immaculate open floor plan and upgrades galore, this 4 bedroom and 3 Full bath spacious home does not disappoint.  Located in the Heart of Florida and just a short drive to all the entertainment that Central Florida has to offer, Haines City offers many local attractions with many running and bike trails, an aquatic center with a competition pool, concerts, dining, and many community events for your enjoyment.  Since this home offers two full master suites, hosting and entertaining will be a breeze.  Sellers are willing to help with closing costs or helping to buy down up to 2 points. Solar panels reduce the energy footprint and lowers your utility cost.  Don't miss this one as it is priced to sell.
